==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea snail
<hw>Sea" snail`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>A small fish of the genus <gen>Liparis</gen>, having a ventral
sucker. It lives among stones and seaweeds.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>Any
small creeping marine gastropod, as the species of <gen>Littorina</gen>,
<gen>Natica</gen>, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sea snake</ent>⟦br⟧
